    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, offering a reliable and comfortable driving experience. The interior is clean and well-kept, though you may find some minor signs of normal use on the upholstery. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, with only a few small stone chips and light scratches consistent with its age. All major systems are functional, making this a solid choice for anyone seeking a dependable car that is ready for the road.",
