      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, offering pristine aesthetics and mechanical integrity that mirror its original showroom delivery. A rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle in peerless, investment-grade condition.",
