    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been treated like royalty and honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or dent to be found\u2014it\u2019s truly in flawless shape. If you\u2019ve been dreaming of a ride that feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it. Come give it a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
