    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with high-pressure double-VANOS and individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains structurally pristine, with no subframe fatigue and a factory-spec suspension that maintains original kinematic integrity. Meticulously preserved with zero mechanical deferment, this is a turnkey investment for the purist seeking an uncompromised driving experience.",
